snippet.title: The Protagonish: Official Launch Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A point-and-click adventure game, where you don't control the adventurer! Play 4 'NPCs' in a medieval fantasy village, and choose to help or hinder the knight in their epic quest...
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2994780/The_Protagonish/

A short game with multiple endings, hand drawn art, fully voice acted and performed on Celtic instruments. Available on Steam and itch.io on October 24th, for Windows, Mac and Linux (inc Steam Deck!). Wishlist today and get notified when it comes out, or follow our channel for exclusive footage and the latest info!

https://www.theprotagonish.com
